311
00:15:12,260 --> 00:15:12,870
You...

312
00:15:13,640 --> 00:15:14,850
You are still alive?

313
00:15:18,750 --> 00:15:19,690
Qiao.

314
00:15:20,710 --> 00:15:21,690
Qiao.

315
00:15:23,640 --> 00:15:24,840
Put me down.

316
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:29,960
Qiao.

317
00:15:33,090 --> 00:15:35,150
