378
00:19:40,530 --> 00:19:41,680
Lu Zizheng.

379
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:44,170
Chunjiao!

380
00:19:46,120 --> 00:19:46,760
Chunjiao!

381
00:19:47,260 --> 00:19:48,240
